text.tspan: The nigerians usually eat rice on Sunday. This typical dish is made with tomatoes and pepper and
can also be prepared with chicken, beef or fish. What is the meaning of rice?
Os nigerianos costumam comer arroz no domingo. Este prato tpico feito com tomate e pimenta e tambm pode ser preparado
com frango, carne ou peixe. Qual o significa de "rice"?
